<h2 id="text-alignment">Text Alignment</h2>

<p>You can quickly change the text alignment of any card‚Äîin its entirety or specific parts‚Äîwith our <a href="/arizona-bootstrap/docs/0.0/utilities/text/#text-alignment">text align classes</a>.</p>

<div class="bd-example">
